{"tid":431163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港足主場迎「大馬」賽前 球迷續噓國歌 有人舉「香港獨立」橫額","createTime":"2017-10-10T12:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T11:36:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86c07da790155a167639715fbdb226c0032ccdfc","tid":431163,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171010/s00006/3e2d1790def4e1b8d8b733f4cd0abeb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171010%2Fs00006%2F3e2d1790def4e1b8d8b733f4cd0abeb7.jpg&h=05358813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港足今晚在香港大球場舉行的亞洲盃外圍賽B組賽事，迎戰馬來西亞前，主場球迷再度噓中國國歌，又有人高舉港獨標語。<br />\n<br />\n港足上周四在旺角大球場友賽老撾賽前奏中國國歌時，再次出現噓國歌場面引來各界迴響，今晚在香港大球場迎戰馬來西亞前，在「香港力量」和「波台黐線佬」等本地球迷組織的104至105區域，部分球迷在賽前奏國歌期間仍有噓國歌，當中有人背向球場，或打交叉手勢，亦有人舉「香港獨立」，及「KIM OUT」橫額，要求港足教練金判坤下台。足總工作人員曾勸阻，但球迷未有理會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171010/s00006/1507637286596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171010%2Fs00006%2F1507637286596&d=g9ZhlBacktmsfUCJb49FixOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=82936758\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171010%2Fs00006%2F1507637286596&h=b9e238ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171010/s00006/1507637286596</a>"},{"pid":"41093ca2e113e3eaeebc33738434eca4875c1391","tid":431163,"uid":154456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}